Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.53,0:00:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,樱花绽放之未来恋梦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.54,0:00:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,天空好蓝 你露出了微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.25,0:00:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不经意的一句话使内心相系
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.32,0:00:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,刚穿上的鞋  敞开门扉的后方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.03,0:00:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,跟你重合的景色使我心动
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.04,0:00:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,樱花绽放之未来恋梦\N加速的心跳无法压抑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.85,0:01:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,两人共同感受  季节不断更替
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.49,0:01:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,无可取代的瞬间\N编织着邂逅的物语
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.40,0:01:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,对纷飞的樱花许下心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.41,0:01:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,向前行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.28,0:01:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,花盛开着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.15,0:01:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,#25 逐渐崩坏的心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.33,0:01:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是…哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.55,0:02:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这是…音梦的梦？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.64,0:02:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,音梦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.91,0:02:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么会有那个戒指呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.35,0:02:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 是我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.98,0:02:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不 或许这是小樱的梦？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.95,0:02:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你不知道么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.09,0:02:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,好漂亮的戒指呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.86,0:02:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,可以借我看一下么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.67,0:02:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.20,0:02:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那个戒指有这么重要么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.08,0:03:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,重要…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.11,0:03:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 这是很重要的戒指
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.61,0:03:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.00,0:03:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,音梦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.43,0:03:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,振作一点 音梦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.71,0:04:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.77,0:04:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你做梦了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.72,0:04:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,音梦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.01,0:04:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,好讨厌的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.39,0:04:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,小樱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.23,0:05:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你还没吃早餐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.04,0:05:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,好像很好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.24,0:05:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这真的是哥哥做的么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.61,0:05:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,因为已经没办法拜托赖子啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.91,0:05:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.28,0:05:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都走掉了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.86,0:05:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,总之在音梦康复之前\N也只好由我来做了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.43,0:05:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不过就算音梦康复\N也还是只能我做就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.43,0:05:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好久没吃音梦的难吃的料理了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.07,0:05:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,没想到还颇怀念的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.94,0:05:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,音梦她会好起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.88,0:05:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.65,0:05:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我有点在意一些地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.45,0:05:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.32,0:06:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然没办法讲得很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.66,0:06:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,音梦是不是有点怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.03,0:06:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,怪怪的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.23,0:06:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不 应该是我多心了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.62,0:06:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,樱花的…？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.01,0:06:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,音梦？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.94,0:06:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,音梦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.95,0:07:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,音梦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.09,0:07:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,音梦 你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.09,0:07:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.30,0:07:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,音梦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.30,0:07:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,音梦 我要开门啰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.87,0:07:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,音梦 你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.61,0:07:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚刚有点头晕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.81,0:07:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你必须好好休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.12,0:07:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,要帮你把早餐端进来么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.05,0:07:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.42,0:07:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,可是我不想吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.13,0:07:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.57,0:07:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,音梦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.70,0:07:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以起来了么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.41,0:07:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,似乎已经好很多了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.44,0:08:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥 我好想吃点甜的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.85,0:08:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,甜食么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.28,0:08:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.59,0:08:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我想吃蛋糕不是和果子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.36,0:08:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,蛋糕我就实在是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.09,0:08:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,所以请你买给我好么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.30,0:08:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,还有冰淇淋和布丁也要喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.30,0:08:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我是个任性又爱吃的公主
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.47,0:08:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.47,0:08:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,会有这样的食欲我也安心了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.94,0:08:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.28,0:08:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉老是让你担心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.95,0:08:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我马上回来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.04,0:09:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.97,0:09:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,小樱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.21,0:09:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我看到烟雾所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.56,0:09:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.37,0:09:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,音梦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.74,0:09:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,音梦的病…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.74,0:09:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,其实都是因为我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.91,0:09:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,小樱…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.42,0:09:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,是我对樱花树许愿的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.20,0:10:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,这是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.13,0:10:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,因为…因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.40,0:10:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,这是骗人的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.14,0:10:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我试着想要放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.08,0:10:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,因为哥哥选择了音梦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.08,0:10:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我试着想要放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.85,0:11:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,可是我的内心深处却在抗拒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.43,0:11:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我心中的某处还在憎恨音梦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.00,0:11:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,可是当我知道音梦生病时
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.07,0:11:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得我必须要想想办法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.21,0:11:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,这是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.84,0:11:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我让实现愿望的樱花枯萎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.72,0:11:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,可是为什么又…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.49,0:11:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不管把哥哥让给谁都可以\N可是就只有小樱不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.86,0:11:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.00,0:11:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道这是为什么么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.00,0:11:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我从小就一直看着哥哥跟小樱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.75,0:12:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,也痛切感觉得到\N小樱有多么喜欢哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.40,0:12:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,所以如果哥哥被小樱抢走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.40,0:12:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我将会永远失去哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.24,0:12:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,想到这里我就好害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.78,0:12:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.19,0:12:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我知道音梦有多喜欢哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.29,0:12:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,所以只有音梦我不愿意让步
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.83,0:12:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我们好像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.57,0:12:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,就像是镜中的另一个自己
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.80,0:13:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,小樱一直看着我\N我也一直看着小樱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.71,0:13:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.81,0:13:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我并不是因为这样\N才想让音梦或哥哥这么痛苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.28,0:13:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.95,0:13:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,这些我都知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.99,0:13:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.96,0:13:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,音梦？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.63,0:13:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,音梦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.60,0:13:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,音梦 你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.60,0:14:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不要过来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.27,0:14:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,音梦 快开门
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.01,0:14:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,音梦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.48,0:14:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不要看！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.49,0:14:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.39,0:14:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你不要看我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.79,0:14:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,是何时开始的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.93,0:14:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,什么时候开始的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.57,0:14:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么没有告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.67,0:14:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.71,0:14:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.67,0:14:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.89,0:14:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,小樱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.70,0:15:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,小樱 你在么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.75,0:15:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,小樱 你在的话就回答我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.96,0:15:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,小樱 音梦她又吐出樱花花瓣了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.56,0:15:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.10,0:15:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我去过奶奶的樱花树那边了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.57,0:15:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,结果本来应该枯萎的樱花树\N却像是失控一样盛开
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.64,0:15:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,就像是在嘲笑我一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.02,0:16:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,小樱 总之你先开门吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.86,0:16:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.13,0:16:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我都已经打算要放弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.73,0:16:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我的内心某处一直羡慕着音梦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.30,0:16:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不会再跟哥哥见面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.27,0:16:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经这么决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.51,0:16:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,小樱…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.65,0:16:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,把门打开吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.91,0:16:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我不要\N看到哥哥我就会改变心意的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.79,0:16:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,小樱…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.26,0:16:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.53,0:16:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么哥哥比我先认识音梦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.80,0:16:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,如果哥哥选择的是我\N事情就不会变成这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.17,0:16:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.51,0:16:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥完全没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.31,0:16:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,做错的人明明是我才对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.31,0:16:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,这样很任性吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.35,0:17:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,小樱…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.18,0:17:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,回去吧 求求你…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.71,0:17:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,午安
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.11,0:17:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,真子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.48,0:17:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你的制服 音梦的我也拿来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.72,0:17:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,杉并
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.65,0:17:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这些东西光靠水越一个人\N随便也能扛个十箱过来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.79,0:17:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不过我还是出马帮忙搬就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.33,0:17:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你就给我少说两句吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.57,0:17:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,对喔 要进入直属班级了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.74,0:17:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,振作一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.20,0:17:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么连朝仓都这个样子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.57,0:18:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.09,0:18:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,音梦 你醒着么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.10,0:18:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.70,0:18:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,真子跟杉并来了 要进去啰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.80,0:18:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,音梦 身体怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.71,0:18:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,音梦的制服我也拿来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.88,0:18:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,想说你看到这个精神会好一点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.82,0:18:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,在姐姐进入直属班级时\N我好羡慕这套制服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.29,0:18:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,音梦你还记得么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.03,0:18:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,有一次音梦来我们家住
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.73,0:19:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,半夜还偷拿姐姐的制服来穿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.40,0:19:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.61,0:19:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,音梦？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.74,0:19:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,真是不敢相信呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.41,0:19:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉上好像昨天升上三年级
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.04,0:19:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,现在竟然已经这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.75,0:19:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,音梦 可惜你没参加毕业典礼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.82,0:19:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不过要赶快痊愈\N然后一起上学喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.36,0:19:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不要 我哪里都不想去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.53,0:19:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我要跟哥哥在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.49,0:19:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下 音梦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.10,0:19:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.40,0:19:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.34,0:19:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我不跟不认识的人一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.84,0:19:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我要跟哥哥在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.41,0:19:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,到底是怎么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.01,0:19:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,是我 我是真子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.18,0:19:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你不认得我了么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.45,0:19:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,音梦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.39,0:19:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,杉并？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.76,0:19:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,总之现在最好不要刺激她
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.10,0:20:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉了 杉并
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.94,0:20:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,他们是谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.18,0:20:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,音梦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.85,0:20:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的想不起来么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.88,0:20:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥 我好怕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.82,0:20:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我好怕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.39,0:20:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,好像哥哥会离我远去一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.62,0:20:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,音梦 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.93,0:20:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.47,0:20:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你放心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.41,0:20:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.38,0:20:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我实在搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.98,0:20:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,看来她好像愈来愈严重了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.92,0:20:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,到底是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.72,0:21:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,可以就这样放着不管么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.02,0:21:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,杉并
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.42,0:21:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,真子 杉并？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.16,0:21:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,芳乃同学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.00,0:21:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.33,0:21:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我想出去旅行一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.40,0:21:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.24,0:21:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,现在留在音梦的身边好么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.54,0:21:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.38,0:21:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,音梦她…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.98,0:21:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,音梦她…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.92,0:21:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,朝仓妹妹的样子很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.92,0:21:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,她好像不认得我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.96,0:21:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,无论是从学校毕业
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.46,0:21:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,还有要一起升学的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.73,0:21:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,她全部都忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.53,0:21:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.87,0:21:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,就是所谓的丧失记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.67,0:21:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.73,0:22:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是…我的心愿？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.74,0:22:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,是我所期盼的？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.11,0:22:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,预告
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.24,0:22:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,音梦、音梦！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.68,0:22:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你在哪里…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.02,0:22:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,音梦丧失记忆？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.52,0:22:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会这样 这是骗人的！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.82,0:22:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.09,0:22:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,这是哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.93,0:22:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我好害怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.93,0:22:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.80,0:22:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,完结篇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.81,0:23:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,从掌心满溢洒落
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.09,0:23:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,有着眼泪颜色的花瓣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.79,0:23:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,若是对风唱出摇曳的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.40,0:23:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,总有一天会传达到你身边么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.34,0:23:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,搜寻片段的记忆之线
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.68,0:23:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,只是希望能在前方见到你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.12,0:23:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,寻找小小脚印而徘徊的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.33,0:23:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,就算明知那里什么都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.80,0:24:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,因为知道我是如此珍惜
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.14,0:24:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,即使已经凋零\N仍能傲于曾经绽放而向前
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.71,0:24:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,如此永远地…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.92,0:24:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,悄悄将你的存在深藏于内心
